Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:39.94,logo2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}SGS曙光社\Nhttp://bbs.sgsub.com/
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.87,0:01:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 很怀念吧 这伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.71,0:01:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得的 你果真是基尔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.66,0:01:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H666666&\b0\pos(319,372)\blur7}来自深渊的呼喊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许在这里死去也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护主人是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会背叛您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 再也不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那种回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.43,0:02:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易 好不容易回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却又…要失去…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挣脱了多鲁达姆的束缚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾 这次就此落幕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这跟我写的剧本不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情期待下次的演出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹·贝萨流士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气息完全消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是真的走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:04:02.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗～艾丽丝 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有受伤…貌似没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的想死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会呢 没可能的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.25,0:04:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.27,0:04:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果 如果我没能停下来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就做好觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我知道你一定会停下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你是基尔的话 绝对…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不相信什么绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 就算有那么一小点也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您不这么觉得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会背叛您
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 不会让任何人伤害你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我相信你的绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不再是你所了解的基尔巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是… 我是基尔巴特·奈特雷伊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈特雷伊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 和贝萨流斯家族水火不容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我是四大公爵之一 奈特雷伊的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不要再像以前那样接近我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经没有那样的资格了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 那家伙在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈特雷伊…为什么又变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 这算哪门子的解释啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他对我来说 是胜于一切的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他解释的机会有过很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也早就知道总有一天会露馅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是没能向他解释
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不像话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人很可能还在 得赶紧回…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里还真是十年都没变呐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么…自然是帮你疗伤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 给我绷带
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.53,0:07:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟我 还有艾达三人公馆探险的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半路上掉到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 还活着吗 基尔巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过对我来说 只是前两天的事情而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么一直不说话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想被你知道改变了的我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是你啊 脱线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改变了 哪方面?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指比我高了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是指会开枪了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过了十年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自然很多事情都不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:09:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我却看不出来有什么改变让你不像你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睁开眼的时候 你离我最近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 刚刚也证明了所谓的「绝对」不是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我吧 到底哪里不像你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到如今 我还深信着那番话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管发生什么 我都会在您身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管经过多久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算两人的立场有所改变
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算成了公爵的人又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确 贝萨流斯和奈特雷伊关系不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 话说在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只不过成了贵族 也别妄想我会放你走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 还是老样子 你这个蛮横的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是背叛了贝萨流斯家族
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此你也能原谅我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 如果你希望如此的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想一直做您的随从
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是如今 我仍想做您的随从
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见 基尔巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 我说的没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 别跟我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你总明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管到哪里 到头来你都会…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你的「阿嵬茨的意识」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你为什么会是艾丽丝?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会是艾丽丝?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:54.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你是…染血黑兔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是梦么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 脸色铁青的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要随便碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.26,0:12:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸦怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让他在坟墓前等着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我们本来就是来调查那座坟墓的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以还是不能没有艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道 我们扔下你 你生气了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.66,0:12:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚这个有点过分哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 你个蠢货!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区仆从 丢下我算是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:52.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜你所赐做了个很不愉快的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我带路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没跟他详细谈过?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 艾丽丝也不太了解这边的情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去听的话 也能大致了解一些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 确实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.63,0:13:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…虽然有这么一说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想整理一下头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能从阿嵬茨出来我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且又能跟基尔在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 还是总觉得很不现实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔 怎么样 找到什么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 要是知道是谁的坟墓就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了吧 艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为声音太小 没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这些树 这些花瓣里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.08,0:14:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点一点聚集着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待着我的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.49,0:14:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道 是那笨兔子的记忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坏孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟着来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在艾丽丝的记忆中出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「阿嵬茨的意识」在看着的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.28,0:16:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记忆的空间开始崩溃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这回可要好好保护他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什么啊 「阿嵬茨的意识」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.38,0:16:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好难受 基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是很清楚 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但应该是创造了阿嵬茨的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.97,0:16:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是潘多拉和巴斯卡瓦一直追寻的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是…那是兔子?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那恐怕是个傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在等你哦 一直
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直 一直
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直 一直
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来接我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我准备了很多娃娃 用这些来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪我说话直到入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗 我亲爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不认识你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个 能不能请你放了艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.61,0:17:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可是个灵体哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是迟早要毁灭你的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很吵!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.45,0:18:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要妨碍我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.54,0:18:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对她一点也不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.17,0:18:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么还要留在她身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和艾丽丝…在一起的理由?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 她连自己是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己出世的理由都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可配不上你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是… 她却把你抢走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.21,0:18:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是没有出世就好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有出世…就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说啊 抛弃那种家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确 如你所说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一点也不了解艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 就是不能放着她不管
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得跟我很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.07,0:19:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能没有艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么依据哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.59,0:20:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是遵循自己的信念而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且啊 虽然很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你啊 似乎是谈不来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.36,0:20:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是难得的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过不巧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在比起玩人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更迷寻宝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:20:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.24,0:21:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.85,0:21:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然放弃我而选择了染血黑兔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.25,0:21:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「阿嵬茨的意识」这么早就来干预了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.77,0:21:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真没想到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过总之 一切都如我们所预计的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧 回潘多拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:21:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.02,0:22:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点…来接我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.92,0:23:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}解开谜团 揭示真相的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.06,0:23:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}奥兹就是「这样」的存在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.92,0:23:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}令人恐怖的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.02,0:23:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}是什么让你如此扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.89,0:23:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}我只剩下不到一年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.18,0:24:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}那句诅咒的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.56,0:24:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}究竟是谁曾向我诉说?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.73,0:24:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&}下回 隐者的提问
